item.title: Aaron & Nicola Keim - It Ain’t Gonna Rain No More - Key of F
item.description:
For Educational Use! By Wendell Hall, 1923. Key of F: F & C7 (C works, fine, too, but use the C7). Performed by Aaron and Nicole Keim, a video resource for "The Ukulele Handbook." Consider buying the book at www.quietamericanmusic.com. Check out the original video at: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TUH5aHTEl3k
Ukulele font from Chordette for Education by ukefarm.com
